verbose_text: Our group previously reported that IL8 and MMPs are elevated in asphyxiated newborn pigs using 100% oxygen instead of 21% [XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR], but these pigs were not as sick and resuscitation was begun at a systolic blood pressure below 20 mmHg, not at asystole.
evidence: MMPs are elevated in asphyxiated newborn pigs
